    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>I</abbr><ex>ovi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>O</abbr><ex>ptimo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>aximo</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Is<lb break="no" n="2"/>is </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Sa<lb break="no" n="2"/>ra<lb break="no" n="3"/>pis </ab></div><div n="4" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Conserva<supplied reason="lost">t</supplied>tori <lb n="2"/>ceteris diis dea<lb break="no" n="3"/>busque e<supplied reason="lost">t</supplied> <lb n="4"/>Genio Iuni Victori<lb break="no" n="5"/>ni co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ularis</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Secionius <lb n="7"/>Senilis b<expan><ex>ene</ex><abbr>f</abbr><ex>iciarius</ex></expan> co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ularis</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/><supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan></supplied> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Zwischen Z.1 u. Z. 2 Büsten von Isis und Serapis; links und rechts sind jeweils die zugehörigen Namen eingemeißelt. Bei der Auffindung war die linke untere Ecke mit dem Beginn der letzten Zeile noch erhalten. (B): AE 1899: Z. 2-6: keine Angabe der Namen Isis, Sarapis; Grimm; Bricault: Z. 4-6: Sa/ra/&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;is; Z. 7: Conserva[to]ri; SIRIS; Bricault: Z. 8: dis; Z. 10: Iunii.</p>
            </div>
